Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.70,0:00:14.22,*Default,Manager,0,0,0,,Big winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.42,0:00:14.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.63,0:00:16.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.50,0:00:20.18,*Default,Asu,0,0,0,,I've won?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.61,0:00:22.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, the third place prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.78,0:00:26.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... third place gets... which one was it again...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.91,0:00:28.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.78,0:00:32.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,Here, the highest quality kind, and it comes as a set.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.79,0:00:34.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,You're happy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.17,0:00:37.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking about it afterwards...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.41,0:00:43.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,This must be a present given to Asu and I from Mother in heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.02,0:00:49.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.78,0:00:53.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Onee-chan. Thank you for your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.35,0:00:54.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,Breakfast is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.89,0:00:56.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.78,0:01:01.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.30,0:01:08.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.00,0:01:11.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine. It's all right, Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.12,0:01:16.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I was a little careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.10,0:01:18.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,That's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.62,0:01:21.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go wash my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.06,0:01:33.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.95,0:01:37.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,Yawning in front of our house is kind of rude, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.94,0:01:39.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.47,0:01:41.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.40,0:01:43.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,See you, Onee-chan will go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.80,0:01:47.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, be careful and watch out for cars!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.12,0:01:49.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.62,0:01:53.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,I let Asu worry about me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.56,0:01:55.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,I have to try harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.08,0:02:01.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,Lately, the neighboring district's newspaper carrier resigned.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.04,0:02:05.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,Because they haven't found anyone yet, the work has been tough lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.19,0:02:08.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.56,0:02:14.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot to tell Asu that
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.04,0:02:17.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,this morning's cucumber was great.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:25.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,The third place prize!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.26,0:02:27.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Asu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:31.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,Third place receives this, and it comes as a set.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.82,0:02:33.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,Prepaid premium cell phones.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.73,0:02:35.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,The card is already in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:38.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,Here, let me help you bag it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.21,0:02:40.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,Are... are you really giving me this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.50,0:02:41.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.33,0:02:57.11,*Default,Preopening,0,0,0,,Mother went to heaven the year she gave birth to Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.59,0:03:00.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,Father left a huge debt after gambling and is now missing,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.54,0:03:04.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,leaving only the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.63,0:03:07.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,The place we live in is
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:09.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,a beaten up 40 year old apartment with one room and no bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.94,0:03:11.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,This is our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.39,0:03:14.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,But, when spring comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:51.35,*Default,Title,0,0,0,,A Day of Emotions, Uneasiness, and Cell Phones.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:56.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Asu, what are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.30,0:04:58.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,The shopping district was having a raffle...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.74,0:05:01.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,These are real, right? Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.77,0:05:03.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.01,0:05:06.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,Cell... Phones?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.42,0:05:08.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,When you say "cell" you mean "mobile" right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:14.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,I've always thought that these things can only be had in some far off world...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.17,0:05:16.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,No... you're exaggerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.17,0:05:17.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:19.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.65,0:05:23.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, how do we use this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:26.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see... first, you turn it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.37,0:05:27.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,Is it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.61,0:05:28.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,Where, where?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:29.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.34,0:05:36.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,Then you choose the payment method. This card has 3000 yen and works for three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:37.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,3000 yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:39.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,Look, that's what it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.48,0:05:41.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,Insert the number, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.62,0:05:42.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.81,0:05:46.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,We can use it now, just like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:48.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, try calling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:50.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,O-okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.41,0:05:55.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,It's ringing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.28,0:05:57.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.79,0:05:59.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.33,0:06:04.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.58,0:06:09.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hang up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:11.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,That was dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.65,0:06:12.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.45,0:06:14.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,Calling like that uses up money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.12,0:06:18.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,3000 yen, eh? We'll have to use it only for important matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.81,0:06:21.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:32.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:36.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,I did it again... Yes, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:39.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,And today, I have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:48.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,If something happens, make sure you call Onee-chan as fast as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:50.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.40,0:06:52.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go on ahead now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.23,0:06:54.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,Today I'm drowsy again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.94,0:07:00.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot it again today...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:03.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,to tell Asu that her tofu miso soup was very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:11.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I have to turn off the cell phone when in school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:13.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.94,0:07:15.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.91,0:07:17.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,Ginko-chan, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.55,0:07:18.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.47,0:07:20.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? You bought a cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.40,0:07:24.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,This? No... It's a prize from the shopping district.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.18,0:07:27.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,Prize...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:33.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-sama has a much better cell phone than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.00,0:07:39.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,Once I'm in middle school, I'll buy one that's as great as Onee-sama's.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:44.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,You should listen when others are talking. What are you doing anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.03,0:07:47.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot how to turn this off... what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.81,0:07:52.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,You don't even know about that? Just press here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:55.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,Ginko-chan, you're so great! Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:58.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,I see Onee-sama do that a lot, so of course I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.65,0:08:01.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,If you have anything else that you don't understand, just ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.52,0:08:03.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,All right, thank you. Well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.18,0:08:08.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,That's nice... a cell pohne.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:17.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,Asu hasn't called yet, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.27,0:08:21.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I should call her...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:26.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan hasn't called yet, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.29,0:08:29.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should call her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:32.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. It's too wasteful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.07,0:08:43.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, maybe something really big happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:45.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,When that happens, I'll need to use the cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:51.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,If I just call her like that, I'll probably run out of minutes when I really need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.99,0:09:00.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you call? If you want to, just call her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:02.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.83,0:09:11.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the mentality of a poor person, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:15.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a week already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.93,0:09:16.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.00,0:09:19.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,And we didn't even use it once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.71,0:09:20.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:23.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,If the three months pass just like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.99,0:09:26.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,That means we've wasted even more money.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:32.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Let's use it more freely afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:34.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,Y... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:38.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,But, don't waste it too much. When we need it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:43.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, if you think like that, you won't call.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:45.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:49.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, the night papers...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.39,0:09:52.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,I have to concentrate. Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.76,0:09:57.30,*Default,,0,0,0,,Turn on, OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:09:59.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,Yamada-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.14,0:09:59.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.77,0:10:01.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,Can you help me for a sec?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:02.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.91,0:10:23.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan didn't pick up. School should have let out already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.97,0:10:26.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if something happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:29.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Ginko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.70,0:10:31.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,So you finally decided to call.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.97,0:10:36.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, because Onee-chan said to use it more freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.29,0:10:40.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask her whether she wanted curry or stewed meat for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.04,0:10:43.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,Calling for such a matter is so boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.82,0:10:48.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, Ginko-chan. if you want, you should give me a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.89,0:10:53.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,Your number... Well, I guess I will when I feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.30,0:10:58.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, what happened to Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:11:00.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,She must be really tired. I'm so worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:09.00,*Default,Eyecatch,0,0,0,,(Our only goal is the before closing sale.)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:17.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,(On paydays we can have a luxurious dinner with three side dishes.)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.03,0:11:25.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,You can't reach her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:27.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:28.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,Connection problems?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.46,0:11:29.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.24,0:11:32.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,When I was at home I could connect to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.87,0:11:34.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,Well then,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:39.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,let me try to place a call to my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.17,0:11:39.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.73,0:11:41.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,Here, let me borrow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:44.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.35,0:11:55.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.18,0:11:58.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-sama, it's Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:12:01.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sorry to give you a call so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:02.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,Are you doing okay right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.96,0:12:06.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yes, yes. That's right, Onee-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:09.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.30,0:12:09.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I heard it was won from a shopping distric raffle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.26,0:12:12.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yes, I think it's the third place prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.56,0:12:13.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:16.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,If only I can be this carefree on a cell phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.29,0:12:20.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.70,0:12:21.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.27,0:12:23.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a time to get emotional.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.88,0:12:26.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,Ah ...um... Ginko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.63,0:12:28.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,If you speak for that long,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.83,0:12:32.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,uh... the 3000 yen will run out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.78,0:12:34.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,She can't hear me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:34.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:39.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right, Onee-sama. And I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.16,0:12:45.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, Onee-chan has been really tired lately. She doesn't say much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.56,0:12:48.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.69,0:12:54.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,It's great that Ginko-chan can talk about so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:56.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,Yamada-san, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.93,0:12:57.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.36,0:13:00.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.23,0:13:02.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, there was a missed call.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:04.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,It must be Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:11.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? It's busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.15,0:13:14.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's the tissue paper from the shopping district.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.24,0:13:16.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.38,0:13:17.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:20.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,You turn the corner at the cigarette store, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.87,0:13:21.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.21,0:13:25.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.68,0:13:27.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, later, Onee-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:29.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.67,0:13:37.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan called, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:44.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,It's Asu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.32,0:13:47.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Asu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:49.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Onee-chan-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:53.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,Asu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.85,0:13:56.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,Asu, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.20,0:14:01.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:02.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,It hung up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:04.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it ran out of battery.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:08.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.98,0:14:13.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,It must be because you didn't charge it fully, so it ran out so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:22.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,The number you have called is not available right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.24,0:14:26.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,I can't connect... what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:28.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.81,0:14:32.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,The number you have called is not...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.16,0:14:35.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Onee-chan-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:40.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,Something must have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.71,0:14:46.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,She must be at the shopping district at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.45,0:14:49.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me! I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.92,0:14:56.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Onee-chan needed something...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.28,0:15:02.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,When she left this morning she looked a little drowsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.51,0:15:05.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's not feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:11.60,*Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to charge the battery you can come to my house...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.71,0:15:13.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.58,0:15:18.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,Normally she'll be at the newspaper route's start off point.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:23.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, Kyo-chan? Now that you mention it, she's not here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:26.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? She's not here? Did she come?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.24,0:15:28.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! What should we do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.13,0:15:29.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.52,0:15:30.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:34.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan really didn't feel well... where can she...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.96,0:15:39.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, that voice from before was Kyo-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.34,0:15:41.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,And she's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.99,0:15:45.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,Asu-chan? I haven't see her today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:46.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:49.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, she should've been here by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.21,0:15:50.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.38,0:15:52.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.71,0:15:58.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange... Asu won't purposely hang up on me ike that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:15:59.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.03,0:16:01.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,She got kidnapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:11.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.58,0:16:15.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that she didn't feel well and went home?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.51,0:16:17.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,The number you have called is not available...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.05,0:16:19.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,Asu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.85,0:16:26.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.61,0:16:34.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,The number you called...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.52,0:16:36.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.58,0:16:43.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, Onee-chan, where are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.64,0:16:48.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:51.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.58,0:16:52.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:58.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, when we finally have cell phones, why doesn't she use it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.23,0:17:01.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.99,0:17:03.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,Asu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.40,0:17:06.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,Asu!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.26,0:17:22.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan!\NAsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:26.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.51,0:17:27.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,Asu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.91,0:17:31.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness! Onee-chan doesn't fall down easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.59,0:17:35.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,Asu too. You weren't kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.46,0:17:39.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:42.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.94,0:17:46.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.27,0:18:01.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,What? The reason I couldn't connect was because your battery ran out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.49,0:18:04.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... along with some other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.47,0:18:08.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,I was also away during that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.12,0:18:12.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,It was just a chance happening, but it was so tiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.02,0:18:14.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,0:18:19.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, that call from before, what were you about to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.64,0:18:26.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Ah, that... I wanted to ask if you wanted curry or stewed meat for dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:31.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,That was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.67,0:18:35.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:37.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,Stewed meat, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.10,0:18:38.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.62,0:18:41.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.96,0:18:43.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.50,0:18:46.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, she's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.61,0:18:48.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Ginko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:51.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,You found your Onee-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.41,0:18:52.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:54.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,That's great, I was worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:18:57.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,Um... that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.75,0:19:00.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for using your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.85,0:19:04.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,Did I trouble you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.16,0:19:07.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,No... not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.54,0:19:11.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I also have a cell phone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.14,0:19:14.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,I see... that's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.82,0:19:16.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.29,0:19:17.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.39,0:19:20.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,Ginko-chan also has a cell phone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.58,0:19:21.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.75,0:19:22.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.90,0:19:27.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,O... Onee-chan... the night newspaper run...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.77,0:19:30.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,You also brought the bicycle out...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.20,0:19:35.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, try your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.01,0:19:37.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make delicious stewed meat for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.29,0:19:46.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.43,0:19:48.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.30,0:19:57.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I forgot to tell Asu that the omelettes were delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.10,0:20:04.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.57,0:20:07.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Asu, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.20,0:20:10.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,What's up? Is something wrong? Did something happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:13.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,The omelettes for breakfast... were really delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.37,0:20:15.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.67,0:20:17.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.70,0:20:20.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I wanted to tell you, Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:24.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything as always, Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.94,0:20:28.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try too hard, Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.05,0:20:32.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,Although it was just a small thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.55,0:20:38.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,these cell phones must have been a present from Mother in heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.87,0:20:43.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,They're probably telling me not to worry too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.66,0:20:47.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,Mother... and Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.30,0:20:52.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, you didn't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:56.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you've already tried fifty times in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.72,0:21:00.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,I know how hard you've been trying, just what did you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.08,0:21:01.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,The cell phones from the third place prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.60,0:21:05.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-sama, we don't have any more tickets for the raffle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.04,0:21:09.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, go buy some things to redeem tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.17,0:21:10.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.10,0:21:13.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,Mister, I still want to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.88,0:21:18.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,Onee-sama, thank you for giving me a cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.35,0:21:20.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.72,0:21:23.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,If you buy one normally, it will be cheaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.42,0:23:00.22,*Default,Preview,0,0,0,,Asu, do you still remember Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.39,0:23:03.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,I remember we had a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.17,0:23:05.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,Binbou Shimai Monogatari.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.99,0:23:08.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,A Day of Colds, Promises and Mother
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.66,0:23:10.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,Please watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.36,0:03:20.80,Default,Opening,0,0,0,,{\an8}Omoitei modorenai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.36,0:03:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though we can't return to our memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.02,0:03:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Kyou wo ikii asuotsukamo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.02,0:03:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,let's seize today and search for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hitorimo ochimo hitorikiri janai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I may be by myself, but I'm not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.96,0:03:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Futarimo ochimo futarikimi janai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.96,0:03:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's only the two of us, we're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:04:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Soredemokoboreru namida no mae ni
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:04:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when seeing my tears about to fall,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.00,0:04:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Egao nashi ugokyuu dekiru noka nai
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.00,0:04:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,can I still smile and take a deep breath?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.84,0:04:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Omoitei modorenai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.84,0:04:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though we can't return to our memories
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.42,0:04:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Kyou wo ikii asuotsukamo
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.42,0:04:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,let's seize today and search for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.26,0:04:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Kagega eno naikimi no owoseki wa kokoro ni aru
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.26,0:04:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That unreachable jewel is there within your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.76,0:04:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Mukai kaze ni shingokyuu
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.76,0:04:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Face the oncoming wind and take a deep breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.26,0:21:50.22,Default,Ending,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ta ainaiosha be iga
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.26,0:21:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when everyday talk
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.83,0:21:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Fuinito gi re ta tokimo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.83,0:21:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,gets interrupted,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.24,0:21:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ko oshite sobani iru dakede
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.24,0:21:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,all I need is you by my side,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.47,0:22:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Anshin tekiru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.47,0:22:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,so I feel safe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.27,0:22:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Obekowo ruwa ni na de ru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.27,0:22:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That kind face of yours
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.70,0:22:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Soyokaze ni tai ne
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.70,0:22:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,is just like a gentle wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.92,0:22:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gyuto gyuto te to te wo tsunaitara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.92,0:22:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We tightly hold each other's hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.40,0:22:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sakamichi wo kage a ga ra wo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.40,0:22:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and run up that hilly path together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.90,0:22:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ashita wa zettai tanoshiine
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.90,0:22:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow will definitely be another happy day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.40,0:22:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nara n de yuko o
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.40,0:22:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us walk shoulder to shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.88,0:22:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gyuto gyuto kaze wo tsu kama e tara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.88,0:22:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I tightly hold on to that flowing wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.34,0:22:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ryuote hirogeto doketai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.34,0:22:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to spread my arms out and give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.89,0:22:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gyuto gyuto ashita no asa atemo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.89,0:22:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We tightly hold each other's hands tomorrow and the day after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.30,0:22:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nara n de yuko iisho ni yuko o
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.30,0:22:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoulder to shoulder, let us walk ahead together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.02,0:23:12.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,